appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Notificatie van een comment of @mention leidt je meteen naar de specifieke comment.

De mobiele versie meer gelijkgetrokken met de desktopversie.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Unsent chat messages are automatically saved. This feature allows you to leave the Place App without retyping your message.
- Profile pictures are visible again in 1-on-1 conversations in the chat. This way, you can clearly see with whom you are chatting in the mobile app.
- Bug fix: users can download documents again that have been sent via chat.
- Up-to-date indication on your timeline. You know which new messages you have not yet read after your last visit with this indication.
